{"tid":1047991,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"「老鬼入黎」咁多年黎、本土快歌黎講，越夜越有機首曲係咪完全超晒班？","createTime":"2019-03-05T10:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T14:24:28.000Z","uid":5006,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"771daf97df9ca068401796ce541ca10374516fd5","tid":1047991,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"一開始成四十秒既前奏已經係世界級<br />\n除左混合左果陣好流行既disco旋律同埋快rap，仲撈埋啲槍聲、仲有堆唔知係咪非洲文既鳩up，聽落竟然又有幾好既化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩段間奏各有特色，尤其是第二段間奏段快rap將成首高潮推到最爆，可想而知啲夜場首歌幾hit<br />\n<br />\n我覺得郭富城首無忌、陳慧琳既花花宇宙前奏雖然聽落唔錯，但變化無咁多，黎黎去去loop果幾個旋律。再次一班，祖兒首隆重登場同鄭秀文既煞科更加普通。鄭伊健既極速就算係咁，又唔算得出色。<br />\n<br />\n講創意同編曲既複雜性，一定係越夜越夜機，仲要間奏唔會翻炒返前奏啲旋律咁濟。首詞就真係唔掂，MV就算係咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係，而家聽返當中既旋律曲風同編曲混音，一啲都唔老土，比十幾年後，而家流行既EDM一啲都唔輸蝕。黎明同雷頌德可唔可以話係香港電音之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無前輩分享下當年夜場越夜越有機有幾hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/egj-Ar5VeD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fegj-Ar5VeD0&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=f879a1de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/egj-Ar5VeD0</a><br />\n越夜越有機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nAXL9RhkR28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnAXL9RhkR28&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=a32ed609\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nAXL9RhkR28</a><br />\n無忌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y4V0l1LflT0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY4V0l1LflT0&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=875a9a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y4V0l1LflT0</a><br />\n花花宇宙"},{"pid":"0d9055ccd16e41570c57cc58174dabba3263d072","tid":1047991,"uid":105114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f359c844ea76fe87a6f585fe361b7cd042bc2088","tid":1047991,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"花花宇宙前無古人後無來者，紅遍全亞洲"},{"pid":"d33281ff2b4cef6f5184dd445156bdb0ff5fa20e","tid":1047991,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f359c844ea76fe87a6f585fe361b7cd042bc2088","tid":1047991,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"花花宇宙前無古人後無來者，紅遍全亞洲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"呢個真 前幾日返大陸做野 起大陸商場仲聽到國語版花花宇宙<br />\n花花宇宙都係呀Mark作曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eafda7368db7fc8163d8b068140d277f1d8efd3","tid":1047991,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"大日子"},{"pid":"29f96cb1905ec5eb0dd999c4f3a8985080ebe80a","tid":1047991,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5eafda7368db7fc8163d8b068140d277f1d8efd3","tid":1047991,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"大日子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"呢首都係正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Em11FJCkrAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEm11FJCkrAk&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=94eb7e67\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Em11FJCkrAk</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽前奏就想un <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千禧年代既快歌真係好屈機"},{"pid":"a2b6e764a022ee0681c9fea0194749cb64c81528","tid":1047991,"uid":242687,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"劉德華首中國人正D<br />\n有氣勢 有熱血"},{"pid":"6c222ae79b5aedcd3caa5b43642b3ee0185b3fa4"